{"tid":2016680,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港共：試題傷害中共人民感情 要求考評局跟進出題機制 從速改善","createTime":"2020-05-14T14:30:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T14:40:02.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8f05ab9c8850dae4fe4ca0a34e451f155b91d6db","tid":2016680,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T14:30:10.000Z","msg":"教育局聲明<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  就今日（五月十四日）香港中學文憑考試（文憑試）歷史科（卷一）考題引起社會極大關注，教育局發言人回應如下：<br />\n<br />\n  「教育局知悉今年文憑試的歷史科有試題附帶極為片面的資料，致試題具引導性，考生可能因而達至偏頗的結論，嚴重傷害了在日本侵華戰爭中受到莫大苦難的國民的感情和尊嚴。教育局對公開試中出現如此設計的試題深感遺憾，並予以譴責。」<br />\n<br />\n  「教育局要求香港考試及評核局嚴肅跟進，向公眾作出合理交代，並全面檢討出題機制，從速改善，以維護文憑試的公平性、公正性及可信性。」<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年5月14日（星期四）<br />\n香港時間22時12分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202005/14/P2020051400792.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202005%2F14%2FP2020051400792.htm&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7gy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=85963ba0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202005/14/P2020051400792.htm</a>"},{"pid":"90d6256e187d175501c24edab303e2808389bcac","tid":2016680,"uid":124410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T14:31:36.000Z","msg":"玻璃心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53b613ce5cfdeb47c4fa8bef14e429ee8dc5a291","tid":2016680,"uid":87780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T14:34:07.000Z","msg":"孫中山同毛澤東都係黐日本起家<br />\n港共唔熟書又喺度奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己老豆姓乜都唔知"},{"pid":"7339e00ae46461121858fb93a4cc417799e81155","tid":2016680,"uid":161726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T14:34:26.000Z","msg":"點條問題出黎大家睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"395f8874357237ff3607dd7e25816b270cd48e2d","tid":2016680,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T14:35:37.000Z","msg":"EAA 前線好黃"},{"pid":"2b547f2a6eb06314513aae17aa2f0142c47bafd8","tid":2016680,"uid":286897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T14:35:54.000Z","msg":"其實教育局係咪想貼題<br />\n出日本都要出侵華<br />\n一定要講一轉先"},{"pid":"9aea4a9f3ba4011b43e622f8dd91f3f990c81776","tid":2016680,"uid":13940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T14:40:02.000Z","msg":"睇黎就快改歷史啦"}]}